Data source 7

Find attached the compressed zip folder.

Unzip and extract the .bak file.

Copy file from the present location and move it to SQL Back up location using this path:

C:\Program Files\Microsoft SQL Server\MSSQL15.MSSQLSERVER\MSSQL\Backup

Paste the .bak file in the Backup folder.

Using the below step, restore the database to your SQL Server instance



Once you have the database accessible in the SQL Management studio,

Go to Power BI Desktop and  select SQL database to import data. Please follow the gif below.
